@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ieejth(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((tmp + (tmp + 0.91 / v2 + 0.04)) - wp.exp(tmp))
    v0 = v1
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.exp(tmp + 0.55)) + (wp.sin(tmp + 0.71) - wp.sin(v2 + 0.34)))
    v0 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.56 - v0 + 0.57)) / ((tmp + 0.91 + tmp + 0.81) - v2))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.sin(0.32))
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.sin(wp.sin(tmp + 0.93)))
    v0 = v2
    tmp = v2
    data[tid] = v0
